== Mashup ==

Mashup is the best icons from various sources. Its like making a mix tape. I also resized and modified icons from SVG to PNG format. Its a collection of highly aesthetic icons, designed to be classy, professional, and functional, not cartoony. Includes a mix of aero, oxygen, glass, crystal, tango, and custom icons.

=== Concept ===
A basic high quality, bold and vibrant set of distinctive icons.
